item.description:

baez9:

Only difference on deltascape is that teleports is in clickingmost.java, from other sources…

That and the fact DeltaScape uses different methods than the basic All-Star…

DeltaScape is an over-rated source way too much.

But that is not the point…you can just post questions on the board and we can answer them…I don’t think many people are going to spoon-feed you over hotmail.
